event.title: Venky's Presents Da High Cookout feat Paraphoniks+OX7GEN
event.description:
This Sunday at the High Spirits Cookout we bring you some of the best electronica and DnB this country has to offer! 
Get ready for Oxy7en with some high-energy, delightfully fluid sets, that seamlessly takes you through every emotion associated with bass heavy music and with Paraphoniks with their real-time music production using modular synthesizers to create a unique raw, edgy sound, yet maintaining a melodic, funky and dancy experience! Now all you need to do is just grab some Beer and BBQ and youve got the perfect Sunday Cookout!

About the Artists:

Ox7gen

OX7GEN is drummer Aditya Ashok's alter ego. Being a drummer adds layers of versatility to his producer avtar. In less than 2 years he has performed at nearly every major festival in the country. OX7GEN has played the closing slot at 2 separate stages for 2 consecutive years at Indias biggest music festival  Bacardi NH7 Weekender. He has performed as a supporting act for some of the biggest international bass artists including London Elektricity, KOAN Sound, Concord Dawn, Dub Phizix & Nymfo to name a few. His performances range from showcasing his material as a producer, to DJ sets to live sets where he collaborates with session musicians to perform his music live. OX7GEN has released 3 EPs with the most recent being Recess, showcasing a sound that he has matured into over the years.

Paraphoniks

Paraphoniks is a Bombay based live electronica act formed in 2015 by Shatrunjai Dewan and Sid Shirodkar. Inspired by many musical styles, the duo tie their disparate influences together by a shared love of modular synthesizers and other electronic instruments. Combining the immediacy and often unpredictable nature of these weapons with more conventional instruments such as guitars and keyboards, Paraphoniks employs a unique approach to both making music and live performance. Paraphoniks released their debut album titled Handwired in 2015. With a few club shows under their belt, the highlight of the year for the act was a prime time slot at The Lost Party 2016. Paraphoniks is currently working on their 2nd album which will be out in the Fall of 2016.

Come home to the music!

event.description:
After such an amazing weekend with great artists across different genres, we decided to make Sunday night a special treat! We bring you an audio-visual experience with Portals on visual duties and Deep Sky Orchestra taking over the music! Let's end the week on a High note! 

About the Artist:

Deep Sky Orchestra
Deep Sky Orchestra is an electronic music project by Deerav Moolani and Shashwat Pradhan. Their project is inspired by the new evolving age of electronic. They launched their debut EP 'Synth Satellite' in 2013. Since then, they have been performing Deep and Future house DJ sets based at all forefront venues in Pune. Moving ahead, they launched their next EP named ' First Avenue' which consists of deep, experimental and future house sounds. 

Portals
Portals Video Mapping is an initiative to create engaging and exciting audio-visual experience by new kids on the block- Naman, Shantanu and Vikrant; a creative breed from various discipline of animation, graphic and product design. Their first project 'DecaGod' is a decagonal portal consisting of 51 sub screens that revolves around light visuals and projection mapped on 3D screen. They believe music is multi-sensorial. You just don't hear it, you feel it and now you see it too!

Come home for a perfect Sunday!
